WEBVTT

00:14:00.017 --> 00:14:02.151
by left-right or politics.

00:14:02.175 --> 00:14:04.506
And now that it's become
this great moral divide,

00:14:04.530 --> 00:14:07.673
there's a lot of evidence
that we're moving to be near people

00:14:07.697 --> 00:14:09.209
who are like us politically.

00:14:09.233 --> 00:14:11.763
It's harder to find somebody
who's on the other side.

00:14:11.787 --> 00:14:14.077
So they're over there, they're far away.

00:14:14.101 --> 00:14:15.671
It's harder to get to know them.

00:14:15.695 --> 00:14:19.919
CA: What would you say to someone
or say to Americans,

00:14:19.943 --> 00:14:21.101
people generally,

00:14:21.125 --> 00:14:23.734
about what we should understand
about each other

00:14:23.758 --> 00:14:27.233
that might help us rethink for a minute

00:14:27.257 --> 00:14:29.460
this "disgust" instinct?